- Previously on "Below Deck"...

00:13.167 --> 00:13.375
- Fist bump.

00:14.917 --> 00:16.625
- You went on a date
with Sierra.

00:16.667 --> 00:17.792
if you're gonna mug me off,
let me know.

00:17.833 --> 00:20.333
F---ing asshole.

00:20.375 --> 00:23.375
- I'm trying to serve the guests
because we're on charter.

00:23.375 --> 00:25.375
Put those flowers
in the walk-in.

00:25.375 --> 00:28.792
- I want Emily to enjoy them,
so I'm trying to preserve them.

00:28.833 --> 00:31.333
- I feel like I'm very much
caught in the middle of this.

00:31.375 --> 00:33.333
I don't want to get
in the way of him and Kate.

00:36.208 --> 00:37.875
- I was frustrated that

00:37.875 --> 00:43.292
Captain had to call over
the radio for service.

00:43.333 --> 00:46.208
Emily and Sierra are taking
advantage of my leniency.

00:46.208 --> 00:47.833
Okay, girls.

00:47.875 --> 00:50.750
- Watch the bow, please.
God damn it!

00:50.750 --> 00:52.375
You're spread just
a little too thin.

00:52.417 --> 00:54.750
Nico, I'm gonna make
you senior deckhand.

00:54.750 --> 00:58.083
I want this last day and a
half here to go flawlessly.

00:58.083 --> 01:00.417
- You gonna come stay
in a hotel with me?

01:00.417 --> 01:02.708
- What?
- Come on. Yeah.

