a preference sheet meeting.

03:58.583 --> 04:00.000
- Roger that,
heading your way now.

04:00.042 --> 04:03.208
- No, Emsters, they'll see you.

04:03.250 --> 04:06.542
- I cannot wait to see who
our last charter group--

04:06.583 --> 04:09.375
once I know who it is,
then it's real.

04:09.417 --> 04:12.917
Oh, the Captain's here.

04:12.917 --> 04:16.750
- Last one--Dawn Gallagher's
the primary.

04:16.750 --> 04:18.875
These are all former models.

04:18.917 --> 04:20.250
They have a lifestyle blog

04:20.292 --> 04:21.708
called "Good Life Gals,"

04:21.750 --> 04:25.625
and they want to do
a photo shoot day one.

04:25.625 --> 04:27.375
They're gonna bring
their own photographer,

04:27.417 --> 04:29.250
and they want to have
a thank you dinner for Dawn

04:29.292 --> 04:31.083
for putting this together.

04:31.125 --> 04:33.083
Nothing to get excited about.

04:33.125 --> 04:34.917
- This could be the girl
of your dreams right here.

04:34.958 --> 04:38.417
- Actually, I feel like there's
a lot of potential here for you.

04:38.458 --> 04:39.958
- Yeah.

04:39.958 --> 04:42.125
I do happen to have some
experience with older women.

04:42.125 --> 04:45.625
When I was 26, I dated
a 42-year-old.

04:45.625 --> 04:48.125
Older women love me.

04:48.125 --> 04:50.875
- I'm kind of sad.
It's our last charter.

04:50.917 --> 04:52.750
- Did you seriously
just say that?

04:52.792 --> 04:55.208
- Yes, I did because,
you know what I wish?

04:55.250 --> 05:04.000
- Okay, I'm done.
- Bye, Captain.

05:04.000 --> 05:06.667
