driving you crazy?

05:10.708 --> 05:11.833
- Yeah.

05:11.875 --> 05:13.500
- My, God.
- What?

05:13.500 --> 05:15.083
- Last time we're doing this.

05:15.125 --> 05:17.500
I just want to get back to,
like, working out and--

05:18.833 --> 05:20.333
- I trust you guys
can make the beds?

05:20.333 --> 05:22.417
- For sure.

05:22.458 --> 05:25.292
- Yeah.

05:25.333 --> 05:28.292
[dreamy music]

05:28.333 --> 05:30.917
♪ ♪

05:30.958 --> 05:32.333
- Kelley, Kelley, Lee.

05:32.333 --> 05:34.667
- Go for Kelley.
- Can you get your deck crew

05:34.667 --> 05:36.833
assembled on the main deck end?
- Yes, sir.

05:36.833 --> 05:38.500
Hey, deck crew,
deck crew can you

05:38.500 --> 05:40.208
