in the game.

05:54.000 --> 05:56.833
These are a bunch of women
that just want to have some fun.

05:56.875 --> 05:58.125
Piece of cake.

05:58.167 --> 06:01.292
- All the toys
set up, everything?

06:01.333 --> 06:03.333
