other than the swimming pool.

06:19.542 --> 06:23.083
Not that I'm mentioning
anything.

06:23.083 --> 06:24.708
Been watching them struggling

06:24.750 --> 06:27.042
with the pool
throughout the whole season...

06:27.083 --> 06:29.708
- That's frigging heavy.
F---.

06:29.750 --> 06:31.917
- F---, there.

06:31.917 --> 06:35.083
- Oh, sh--. Damn it, man.
- F---.

06:35.083 --> 06:37.542
