F---.

06:37.583 --> 06:39.417
- I doubt they'll
ever get it right.

06:39.417 --> 06:42.375
You know, take a page
out of Kate's playbook.

06:42.417 --> 06:44.875
Ben doesn't have a certain item
in the galley,

06:44.917 --> 06:47.250
Kate just steers them
away from it.

06:47.250 --> 06:49.583
- Okay.
- You grab Kate's playbook,

06:49.583 --> 06:51.667
