07:54.667 --> 07:56.125
Always have your radios on,

07:56.167 --> 07:57.500
especially during
dinner service,

07:57.500 --> 07:59.333
when you're doing turn-downs.

07:59.333 --> 08:02.833
Sierra, if you could focus on--
like, when you wash the dishes,

08:02.833 --> 08:04.292
I know you like
to leave them drying.

08:04.333 --> 08:06.083
- Yeah?
- But if we get rough seas,

08:06.125 --> 08:08.833
