just dry them and put them away.

08:08.833 --> 08:11.500
- I feel like Emily
and I have done a great job,

08:11.500 --> 08:13.458
and I have no clue
where this is coming from.

08:13.500 --> 08:15.583
- Emily, you take
so much initiative,

08:15.625 --> 08:18.083
but when you come back
from break, on your radios,

08:18.125 --> 08:19.833
you can just say,
"Kate, I'm back,"

08:19.833 --> 08:21.333
especially during
dinner service,

08:21.333 --> 08:24.250
'cause it could save us work
in the long run.

08:24.292 --> 08:26.250
- I take great pride in my job

08:26.292 --> 08:27.958
and doing it
to the best of my ability.

08:28.000 --> 08:30.500
So Kate's comment
is pretty annoying.

08:30.542 --> 08:31.792
- That's all.

08:31.833 --> 08:33.375
