or earlier than that.

08:49.042 --> 08:50.542
- Yeah, yeah, 'cause I think,

08:50.542 --> 08:52.875
yeah, I--one of us
should be on earlies.

08:57.333 --> 08:59.875
All right, we're on to
something here aren't we?

08:59.875 --> 09:02.208
- Only took us six weeks.

09:02.208 --> 09:04.000
- Lauren, Lauren to Kelley.

09:06.208 --> 09:08.042
- Emily, Emily, Kate.

09:08.042 --> 09:10.208
- You're a little tense,
but you're in good shape, but...

09:10.250 --> 09:12.583
- What do you mean good shape?
What does--

09:12.583 --> 09:14.875
- As in everything seems
to be working right.

09:14.917 --> 09:16.667
- Emily, Emily, Kate.
- Our people don't like us.

09:16.708 --> 09:20.083
- Lauren, Lauren to Kelley.

09:20.083 --> 09:23.417
- You're so naughty.

09:23.417 --> 09:25.167
- I don't know why
nobody carries their radio.

09:25.208 --> 09:28.000
